&lt;h1 id="were-at-the-beginning-of-an-infinity-of-knowledge"&gt;We’re at the Beginning of an Infinity of Knowledge&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mar 15 2021&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;
The difference with &lt;em&gt;The Beginning of Infinity&lt;/em&gt; is you&amp;rsquo;re getting a worldview. You&amp;rsquo;re not getting the standard take from physicists about how to understand quantum theory. You&amp;rsquo;re not getting the standard take of how to understand knowledge from philosophers. And you&amp;rsquo;re certainly not getting the standard take of how to understand mathematics from mathematicians.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>